---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import ProcessRail from "../../components/ProcessRail.astro";
---

<Layout lang="en" title="MIM Process | TANCHIN" description="Metal Injection Molding combines powder metallurgy and injection molding for complex precision parts." active="process">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">MIM Process</p>
    <h1>From powder to manufacturable precision metal parts</h1>
    <p>MIM compounds metal powder and binder into injectable feedstock, then uses injection molding, debinding, sintering, and finishing to produce dense metal components.</p>
  </section>
  <ProcessRail lang="en" />
  <section class="section narrow content-grid">
    <div class="feature-panel">
      <h2>Good fit for MIM</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Complex geometry with high machining cost</li>
        <li>Small to medium precision metal components</li>
        <li>Material flexibility and dimensional stability</li>
        <li>Finishing, heat treatment, or surface processing needs</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-panel">
      <h2>Development flow</h2>
      <p>We evaluate drawings, material requirements, tolerances, volume, and application conditions to determine MIM feasibility and plan sampling through production.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
